This is the edited version of   aim_bridge_AH   (because the old one didn't work) I changed it a lot. Both maps are mine that's why I changed it.

NOTE* In the screenshots it may look a little dark but trust me it's like full daylight out there the only dark spots are caused by shadows from the boxes. Ther'es plenty of light.


I may be making a night-time version later but I'm not sure so if you like night time maps and you like this map keep your eyes out it'll probably be titled  fy_sea-portnight_AH

or fy_seaside-portnight



HOPE YOU ENJOY!
